## Summary

These changes will add:

1. A DataExplorer component under the search card on the Home page
2. The ability to switch between ACS and FBI data sources via dropdown
3. Appropriate input fields for each data source's parameters
4. A scrollable table to display results
5. API service to fetch data from your backend endpoints

The UI will allow users to:
1. Select the data source (ACS or FBI)
2. Enter the required parameters
3. Submit the query
4. View the results in a scrollable table

All components use your existing Button component and follow a similar styling pattern to your existing components. The table is designed to be scrollable both horizontally and vertically to handle any amount of data.

